## 📱 Smartphone Bluetooth Layout

When the FlySky remote goes offline, download any standard Bluetooth RC Controller app and assign these variables:

### 🏃 Driving Operations
- `F` / `B` : Move Forward / Move Backward
- `L` / `R` : Turn Left / Turn Right
- `S` / `D` : Hard Stop / Electronic Brake

### 📐 Tactical Diagonal Turns (Soccer Special)
- `G` : Forward Left Sharp Cut (Left Motor at 10% speed)
- `I` : Forward Right Sharp Cut (Right Motor at 10% speed)
- `H` : Backward Left Sharp Cut (Left Motor at -10% speed)
- `J` : Backward Right Sharp Cut (Right Motor at -10% speed)

### 📊 App Speed Slider Codes
- Supports step-less configuration keys `0` (Stop) through `9` ($90\%$ speed) up to `q` (Maximum $100\%$ Speed).

